{"type":"question","id":20084,"title":"官方“辟谣”来了，永久居住或为谣言，各位怎么看？","uid":36074,"topics":[1717,2225,161,7038],"contents":"刚才还逛一遍确定没有人已经发了<br>\n<br>\n刚才刷空间，有人将抖音上的官方截图发表出来，最近外国人永久居住条例中“联姻”为营销号的谣言，而在此QQ号的大力引导下，营销号再一次被攻击，各位怎么看？<br>\n我觉得典型的辟谣辟一半，抓不到重点，现在又弄得好像整个条例都是假的一样，是否已经开始混战，本身条例还是有，黑人是造谣，但是韭菜们往往就是抓不住重点，包括这个所谓的辟谣，发了跟没发一样<br>\n<br>\n一一一一一一一一一一<br>\n<br>\n我这么起标题，虽然会觉得我是标题党，但觉得联姻本身就不是重点，这种造谣式辟谣，就怕更多韭菜不关注原来的问题<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/9ZslytC.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9ZslytC.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/9ZslytC.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/8vf3A00.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8vf3A00.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/8vf3A00.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/SXQFrYC.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SXQFrYC.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/SXQFrYC.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/9wvDWge.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9wvDWge.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/9wvDWge.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/hy3SWX4.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hy3SWX4.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/hy3SWX4.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-03-03","agreeCount":6,"discussionCount":4}